EN: Maintaining his new car costs a lot every month.

ZH: 这次会议的准备工作耗费了很多时间。
EN: The preparation for this meeting has taken up a lot of time.

ZH: 她每天花费很多时间在社交媒体上。
EN: She spends a lot of time on social media every day.

